Interface GobblinInstanceLauncher

  • All Superinterfaces:

    @Alpha
public interface GobblinInstanceLauncher
extends Service, Configurable, GobblinInstanceEnvironment
    Main class instantiated by the JVM or running framework. Reads application level configurations, instantiates and runs the Gobblin instance driver.
